										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>This is it!  Today, <a href="book-two-trick/">Trick</a> is officially available on <a title="Get the Kindle or Print version!" href="http://www.amazon.com/Clockwork-Twist-Trick-Emily-Thompson-ebook/dp/B00HTQB43U/" target="_blank">Amazon.com</a>, <a title="Get the paperback!" href="https://www.createspace.com/4609008" target="_blank">Createspace.com</a>, and <a title="Get the eBook in any format!" href="http://www.smashwords.com/books/view/395908" target="_blank">Smashwords.com</a>.  Get you copy today!</p>
<p><a href="http://www.amazon.com/Clockwork-Twist-Trick-Emily-Thompson-ebook/dp/B00HTQB43U/ref=la_B00BXOP6AG_1_3?s=books&amp;ie=UTF8&amp;qid=1389640840&amp;sr=1-3" target="_blank"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="alignleft size-medium wp-image-1100" alt="Trick cover proof 4 front" src="http://192.185.17.126/~cwtwist/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/trick-cover-proof-4-front.jpg?w=201" width="201" height="300" srcset="https://clockworktwist.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/trick-cover-proof-4-front.jpg 1644w, https://clockworktwist.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/trick-cover-proof-4-front-201x300.jpg 201w, https://clockworktwist.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/trick-cover-proof-4-front-686x1024.jpg 686w" sizes="(max-width: 201px) 100vw, 201px" /></a></p>
<p style="text-align:center;"><strong>Clockwork Twist : Trick is NOW available!!</strong><br />
<strong>Click the logos below to buy the paperback for $12.00 at</strong></p>
<p style="text-align:center;"><a href="http://www.amazon.com/Clockwork-Twist-Book-Two-Trick/dp/1494938812/" target="_blank"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" alt="" src="http://library.corporate-ir.net/library/17/176/176060/mediaitems/93/a.com_logo_RGB.jpg" width="181" height="53" /></a><a href="https://www.createspace.com/4609008" target="_blank"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" alt="" src="https://ssl.images-createspace.com/csp/Special/Img/logo-csp-no-tm.png" width="110" height="52" /></a></p>
<p style="text-align:center;"><strong>Buy the eBook for $2.99 at</strong></p>
<p style="text-align:center;"><a href="http://www.amazon.com/Clockwork-Twist-Trick-Emily-Thompson-ebook/dp/B00HTQB43U/" target="_blank"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" alt="" src="http://media.corporate-ir.net/media_files/irol/17/176060/KindleLogos/Kindlelogo/scr2555-proj697-a-kindle-logo-rgb-lg.jpg" width="148" height="40" /></a>  <a href="http://www.smashwords.com/books/view/395908" target="_blank"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" alt="" src="https://dwtr67e3ikfml.cloudfront.net/static/1/swlogo.png" width="160" height="43" /></a></p>
<p style="text-align:left;">As I mentioned earlier, the book will become available in the iBookstore, Barnes&amp;Noble, and other retailers in the coming weeks.  Things take a little while to roll out.  While we&#8217;re waiting, check out the shiny new <a href="http://www.goodreads.com/book/show/20520309-trick" target="_blank">Goodreads </a>page!</p>
<p style="text-align:left;">And thank you, once again, to everyone who has gone out of their way to offer support to this series.  You are the ones who make these stories matter.  Let&#8217;s get our lovely little Twist farther into the world, shall we?  Please remember to <a href="https://www.facebook.com/sharer/sharer.php?u=https://www.facebook.com/CWTwist" target="_blank">share</a>, <a href="http://www.facebook.com/CWTwist" target="_blank">like</a>, <a href="http://ctt.ec/qr_b3" target="_blank">Tweet</a>,Tumbl, review and lend!</p>
]]></content:encoded>
					
