&#8211; <a href="http://clockworktwist.com/trick-chpt-3/">Chapter 3</a> &#8211;</h3>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p><span style="color:#000000;">As always, remember that this book will hit on-line stores on Tuesday, January 14th.  And this time, 3 chapters isn&#8217;t all you&#8217;re going to get!</span></p>
<p><span style="color:#000000;">That&#8217;s right, I&#8217;m going to post the 4th and 5th chapters right here on this blog, one per week, up until the book&#8217;s release.  There <em>might</em> also be an opportunity for some very lucky, very lovely dears to get a *cough* free copy of the whole eBook a bit early&#8230;  So, be sure to keep an eye on the old <a href="http://www.facebook.com/CWTwist" target="_blank">Facebook</a>, <a href="http://twitter.com/CWTwist" target="_blank">Twitter</a>, <a href="http://cwtwist.tumblr.com/" target="_blank">Tumblr</a>, or blog to find out about all of the exciting developments!</span></p>
<p><span style="color:#000000;"><a title="Book two : Trick" href="http://clockworktwist.com/book-two-trick/">Click here</a> for a quick synopsis. (no spoilers, I promise.)</span></p>
